5. Difference between async/await and normal method?

Expected Answer

Async methods:

Do non-blocking operations

Free the thread while waiting

Improve scalability in web apps


Example:

public async Task<string> GetData()
{
    var result = await httpClient.GetStringAsync(url);
    return result;
}

Important point

Async improves scalability, not speed.


