10. SQL Question (Very Effective)

Ask this:

Employees Table

Id	Name	Salary	Department



Question

Write SQL to find 2nd highest salary.

Expected Answer

Method 1

SELECT MAX(Salary)
FROM Employees
WHERE Salary < (SELECT MAX(Salary) FROM Employees);

Method 2

SELECT Salary
FROM Employees
ORDER BY Salary DESC
OFFSET 1 ROW FETCH NEXT 1 ROW ONLY;


