Simple Coding Question (Best Interview Question)

Ask candidate to write:

Check if number is Prime

Expected Answer

bool IsPrime(int number)
{
    if (number <= 1) return false;

    for(int i=2; i<=Math.Sqrt(number); i++)
    {
        if(number % i == 0)
            return false;
    }

    return true;
}


